reviewText: I could go on, and on about Travis, I am so happy for him, he has a Beautiful wife Theresa and 3 beautiful children and I was fortunate to have met the only entertainer I ever wanted to meet and so dreams do come true.....keep dreaming
Travis is a great entertainer, when you buy any of Travis's videos their all amazing talent, Travis is a one man show, his cds, videos are all worth buying  Thank you
i think it was one of his finest works to date.  He delivered a great performance as he always does.  He is a true rock and roll-redneck country asset.
